450
00:58:18,828 --> 00:58:22,025
Rekao mi je da je njegov gospodar 
bio princ ovoga sveta.

451
00:58:23,933 --> 00:58:25,833
Mislis na davola?

452
00:58:25,935 --> 00:58:29,234
Ko jos moze da kontrolise senke?

453
00:58:33,543 --> 00:58:35,010
Vraticu se.

454
00:58:35,111 --> 00:58:36,976
Obecala sam.

455
00:59:04,107 --> 00:59:06,200
Izvini, Toby.

456
00:59:07,844 --> 00:59:09,106
Skloni se od mene.

457
00:59:09,212 --> 00:59:12,181
Nikad te necu povrediti.

458
00:59:12,282 --> 00:59:14,147
Skidaj svoje zle oci od mene.

459
00:59:14,250 --> 00:59:15,148
Toby?

460
00:59:15,251 --> 00:59:18,948
Julia, spasi sebe!
Dalje!

461
00:59:19,055 --> 00:59:20,682
Toby, ovo je jako zabrinjavajuce

462
00:59:20,790 --> 00:59:25,124
da imas takvo nepoverenje i antipatiju 
prema meni.

463
00:59:25,228 --> 00:59:28,322
Ali sam siguran , da ces razumeti
da dok si tu ,

464
00:59:28,431 --> 00:59:32,527
Nastavicu tretman tvoje bolesti 
najbolje sto znam.

465
00:59:32,635 --> 00:59:33,329
Sally.

466
00:59:35,672 --> 00:59:36,866
Ne!

467
00:59:36,973 --> 00:59:38,770
Ne!

468
01:00:10,506 --> 01:00:12,337
Dobro vece, Toby.

469
01:00:12,442 --> 01:00:14,205
Toby?

470
01:00:16,746 --> 01:00:19,977
No , sad si zapalio svoje brodove,
sine.

471
01:00:20,083 --> 01:00:22,483
Bilo sta kazes Juliji ,
ona ce misliti...

472
01:00:22,585 --> 01:00:26,419
"Jadan Hal.
Kakva vremena mi sad zivimo."

473
01:00:28,391 --> 01:00:30,450
